v 0.0.0.2
-   added support for Manjaro Linux
-   system-update wont sync the repo (pacman -Su) if started with paramter -u
-   pakman will use this parameter if there are updates known for pacman managed packages
     it will still run pacman -Syu if there are no updates visible in the gui (foreign packages excluded) 

